Package: checkmydois
Title: Verify your public research outpus are available by DOI
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Ross", "Mounce", email = "ross.mounce@gmail.com",
                    role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Daniel", "Himmelstein",
                    email = "daniel.himmelstein@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description:
  R code to check that the DOIs of your own authored research
  outputs (not just articles!) aren't 404'ing. This leverages
  your ORCID profile and your list of public works. (Public
  works only)
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: MIT
Imports:
  httr,
  dplyr,
  rorcid,
  readr
LazyData: true
